    {
      "id": "efa38b4a_eda0c2e3",
      "file_path": "release-notes.rst",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 6,
      "message": "This is more detailed than what I was expecting - this will be better suited under VEScollector RTD doc folder (https://git.onap.org/dcaegen2/tree/docs/sections/services/ves-http) to track released container. I would also remove ONAP release details as they will be maintained globally (like rls date/name). The release date instead can reference the date when VES container was released (or self-release).\n\nOn this repo, we could have more simpler version changelog to identify the jira/issues fixed with specific version update (similar to \nhttps://git.onap.org/dcaegen2/platform/configbinding/tree/Changelog.md)",
      "author": {
